<h3><span id="Prose_et_po.C3.A9sie"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Prose_et_poésie">Prose et poésie</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Harold_Pinter&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=15" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Prose et poésie">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Harold_Pinter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Modifier la section : Prose et poésie">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div style="column-width:24em;column-gap:1em;" class="colonnes">
