.cz/jn19990006574">Bibliothèque nationale tchèque</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://urn.bn.pt/nca/unimarc-authorities/txt?id=90492">Bibliothèque nationale du Portugal</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n79-125182">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
